SYNOPSIS
    UI and REST api to swat <https://github.com/melezhik/swat> engine.

Features List
  UI
    *   list of available / installed swat packages

    *   list of local packages

    *   install/update/remove site package

    *   run swat tests

  RESTAPI
    *   run swat test ( local/swat package ) against a given host and return
        result in required format ( TAP / nagios )

INSTALL
        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

USAGE
        # run swatapi server

        $ swatapi -d

HOME PAGE
    https://github.com/melezhik/swatapi

